<section id="slide18">
 <title>Slide 18:  Important Questions to Consider
 </title>

<list id="list18" list-type="enumerated">
  <item> How do we get more women into the STEM recruitment pool?
     <list id="list18a" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>How do we increase our acceptance rates?
        </item>
        <item>How will we know when we have done a “good job”?
        </item>
     </list>
  </item>
  <item> Why do the climate differences exist?
     <list id="list18b" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Is this a general phenomenon or is it something    particular about Rice University? 
        </item>
        <item>What can we do to reduce these differences and increase the positive climate that women experience? Will we see changes in our next survey (scheduled for next year)?
        </item>
     </list>
  </item>
</list>

</section>

